# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — all three operators across all eight classes in one table
#
# Cross-product of 8 classes × 3 operators = 24 rows confirming full absence
# of numeric unary slots in the multiprocessing public API surface.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

